<L>__{interior ballroom night}
<A>__{twenty five dancing couples, fifty guests, ten servants, full orchestra. as the music slows a little, we see a masquerade ball in progress. a crowded room of dancers is executing the slow portion of a dance fashionable in the early 1820's.}
<L>__{exterior street outside salieri's house night}
<A>__{as the fast music returns, we see old salieri being carried out of his house on a stretcher by two attendants, and placed in a horse drawn wagon under the supervision of a middle aged doctor in a tall hat. this is doctor gulden. he gets in beside his patient. the driver whips up the horse, and the wagon dashes off through the still falling snow.}
